  <title>English Joke</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>English Joke</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Popup Box"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Joke: A dwarf clairvoyant escaped from jail. The police put out a statement that there is a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">&apos;Small Medium at Large&apos;</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Native English speakers understand this Joke. &#160;</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">To explain to speakers of English as a second language...</para>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed">A Dwarf is a &apos;Small Person&apos;. </li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed">A &apos;Clairvoyant&apos; (a person who can foretell the future) is also &apos;a Medium&apos;.</li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed">A person who has &apos;escaped from jail&apos; is someone who is &apos;at large&apos;, especially a Police term.</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Small, Medium </text><text styleclass="Popup Box">and</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small"> Large</text> are all related to size, of course.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">So, when the Police say: <text styleclass="VariableName-small">&apos;A Small Medium is at Large&apos;,</text> it is funny because the words are all size related yet the phrase actually means something entirely different. It is a play on words. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">It also explains why translating between languages is sometimes not easy.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
</topic>
